1
00:01:38,500 --> 00:01:44,300
"Unfold"

2
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:47,500
(Episode 8)

3
00:02:04,625 --> 00:02:06,291
If Yu Guangming wanted to kill Bai Che,

4
00:02:06,458 --> 00:02:08,138
he wouldn't have gone to all this trouble.

5
00:02:09,625 --> 00:02:11,500
He just wants to clean up his mess

6
00:02:11,666 --> 00:02:12,708
so he has no loose ends.

7
00:02:13,500 --> 00:02:14,500
It's not that simple.

8
00:02:15,083 --> 00:02:16,083
Wake up.

9
00:02:21,375 --> 00:02:23,375
I think I met him twenty years ago.

10
00:02:29,041 --> 00:02:31,250
Back then, Lao Bai rounded up those kids

11
00:02:31,458 --> 00:02:32,618
and locked them in dog cages.

12
00:02:33,208 --> 00:02:34,888
He was burning up with a 104-degree fever.

13
00:02:35,458 --> 00:02:37,058
I was the one who gave him his medicine.

14
00:02:37,666 --> 00:02:38,666
So,

15
00:02:38,916 --> 00:02:40,676
you've always hated
this business of theirs.

16
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:43,000
Bullshit.

17
00:02:49,416 --> 00:02:50,665
A bunch of filthy kids running around you

18
00:02:50,666 --> 00:02:51,541
all day long.

19
00:02:51,541 --> 00:02:52,541
Who would like that?

20
00:02:53,750 --> 00:02:54,990
But you still couldn't bear it,

21
00:02:55,500 --> 00:02:56,583
so you wanted to help them.

22
00:03:00,541 --> 00:03:01,375
Three years ago,

23
00:03:01,541 --> 00:03:03,166
you knew Lao Bai sent me here.

24
00:03:03,625 --> 00:03:04,833
Why did you keep me?

25
00:03:24,125 --> 00:03:25,125
Bai Che,

26
00:03:25,166 --> 00:03:26,166
do you remember me?

27
00:03:29,375 --> 00:03:30,375
I don't know you.

28
00:03:31,208 --> 00:03:32,333
Of course you don't.

29
00:03:33,083 --> 00:03:34,415
Back then, you were locked in a cage

30
00:03:34,416 --> 00:03:35,500
like a dog.

31
00:03:35,916 --> 00:03:37,791
You were dying of a 104-degree fever.

32
00:03:38,375 --> 00:03:39,815
If I hadn't given you that medicine,

33
00:03:39,875 --> 00:03:40,916
you'd be dead by now.

34
00:03:41,958 --> 00:03:42,958
Let me go!

35
00:03:44,458 --> 00:03:47,166
That's exactly how I
pried your mouth open.

36
00:03:49,833 --> 00:03:51,708
Get a pen and inkpad. Make him sign.

37
00:03:55,750 --> 00:03:56,750
Don't move!

38
00:04:00,791 --> 00:04:01,416
Bai Che!

39
00:04:01,625 --> 00:04:02,333
Bai Che!

40
00:04:02,500 --> 00:04:03,500
Zhou Chen!

41
00:04:06,208 --> 00:04:06,833
What is he doing here?

42
00:04:06,958 --> 00:04:07,708
Let Bai Che go!

43
00:04:07,791 --> 00:04:08,166
Don't move!

44
00:04:08,500 --> 00:04:09,500
Stay back!

45
00:04:09,875 --> 00:04:10,708
Back off!

46
00:04:10,875 --> 00:04:12,958
Or Bai Che is dead.

47
00:04:19,625 --> 00:04:20,833
Who sent you?

48
00:04:22,833 --> 00:04:24,333
Someone texted me.

49
00:04:25,125 --> 00:04:27,500
You lunatics who play with human lives

50
00:04:28,125 --> 00:04:29,833
will get what's coming to you.

51
00:04:31,250 --> 00:04:32,530
How much is a life worth anyway?

52
00:04:33,166 --> 00:04:34,708
This city went mad a long time ago.

53
00:04:35,291 --> 00:04:36,750
If not for us lunatics,

54
00:04:37,083 --> 00:04:39,203
where would that little
girl's organs have come from?

55
00:04:39,333 --> 00:04:40,333
Oh, right.

56
00:04:40,666 --> 00:04:41,875
You played a part in it too,

57
00:04:42,208 --> 00:04:42,625
Bai Che.

58
00:04:42,750 --> 00:04:43,750
Shut up!

59
00:04:44,041 --> 00:04:45,291
I'm nothing like you.

60
00:04:46,625 --> 00:04:47,333
And you,

61
00:04:47,334 --> 00:04:48,375
Zhou, the great saint.

62
00:04:51,166 --> 00:04:52,916
Do you really think you're a savior?

63
00:04:54,750 --> 00:04:56,041
That little girl's father

64
00:04:56,833 --> 00:04:57,833
contacted us on his own.

65
00:04:58,750 --> 00:04:59,875
He was in debt,

66
00:05:00,166 --> 00:05:01,286
so he jumped off a building.

67
00:05:02,833 --> 00:05:04,625
You happily went to arrange the transplant.

68
00:05:05,166 --> 00:05:06,166
You saved one life,

69
00:05:07,916 --> 00:05:08,916
but you killed another.

70
00:05:13,291 --> 00:05:14,333
You want to silence us

71
00:05:15,291 --> 00:05:15,958
just because we know

72
00:05:15,959 --> 00:05:17,333
too many of your secrets?

73
00:05:19,041 --> 00:05:20,281
Why don't you check your phone?

74
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:22,041
Right now, the whole city

75
00:05:23,041 --> 00:05:24,541
is talking about what you've done.

76
00:05:25,083 --> 00:05:26,843
Do you think Mayor
Yu can still protect you?

77
00:05:28,333 --> 00:05:29,583
Do I need protection?

78
00:05:30,541 --> 00:05:32,208
I just want to sell the port and leave.

79
00:05:32,291 --> 00:05:34,041
I never wanted to kill anyone.

80
00:05:34,541 --> 00:05:36,517
But the fact that Mayor
Yu let you find this place

81
00:05:36,541 --> 00:05:38,458
means he doesn't just want to kill Bai Che.

82
00:05:39,375 --> 00:05:40,541
He wants to kill you too.

83
00:05:47,541 --> 00:05:48,833
Do you think selling the port

84
00:05:49,208 --> 00:05:50,458
and giving Mayor Yu a cut

85
00:05:50,916 --> 00:05:52,083
will make him let you go?

86
00:05:53,333 --> 00:05:53,916
You know

87
00:05:53,917 --> 00:05:55,125
far too much.

88
00:05:55,916 --> 00:05:56,666
What makes you think

89
00:05:56,667 --> 00:05:57,747
you can get away scot-free?

90
00:05:59,541 --> 00:06:00,583
How about this?

91
00:06:05,750 --> 00:06:07,166
"Mayor Yu

92
00:06:07,958 --> 00:06:08,625
hired a hitman

93
00:06:08,626 --> 00:06:10,346
to kill the eldest son of the Zhou family."

94
00:06:10,375 --> 00:06:11,415
Sensational enough, right?

95
00:06:12,125 --> 00:06:13,125
Once we kill you

96
00:06:13,291 --> 00:06:15,083
and get this signed contract,

97
00:06:15,333 --> 00:06:16,583
we'll leak the news.

98
00:06:17,125 --> 00:06:18,205
Do you still think we can't

99
00:06:18,291 --> 00:06:19,291
get away scot-free?

100
00:06:22,208 --> 00:06:23,208
Sign it.

101
00:06:27,875 --> 00:06:28,875
Let Zhou Chen go,

102
00:06:29,625 --> 00:06:30,625
and I'll sign.

103
00:06:30,791 --> 00:06:31,416
Bai Che,

104
00:06:31,791 --> 00:06:32,791
don't!

105
00:06:45,458 --> 00:06:46,583
Let him go.

106
00:06:47,041 --> 00:06:48,375
I'll be your hostage.

107
00:06:50,708 --> 00:06:51,125
Zhou Chen,

108
00:06:51,208 --> 00:06:52,208
don't...!

109
00:06:52,500 --> 00:06:53,790
What makes you think

110
00:06:53,791 --> 00:06:55,041
I need a hostage?

111
00:06:56,750 --> 00:06:58,166
The Zhous aren't stupid.

112
00:06:58,791 --> 00:07:00,711
Mayor Yu is begging
everyone for help right now.

113
00:07:01,125 --> 00:07:02,165
Only with me in your hands

114
00:07:02,166 --> 00:07:03,915
can you force the Zhous
to give you a green light

115
00:07:03,916 --> 00:07:05,625
to leave here safely.

116
00:07:05,708 --> 00:07:06,416
Zhou Chen,

117
00:07:06,541 --> 00:07:07,541
don't...!

118
00:07:07,916 --> 00:07:08,916
Don't fucking move.

119
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:11,000
Tie him up.

120
00:07:26,958 --> 00:07:27,958
Zhou Chen,

121
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:33,208
I'm not worth this.

122
00:07:35,875 --> 00:07:38,208
Don't worry, I didn't lie to you.

123
00:07:38,708 --> 00:07:39,948
And I didn't lie to him either.

124
00:07:40,541 --> 00:07:41,833
We'll all be fine.

125
00:07:53,875 --> 00:07:54,875
Zhao Lingye,

126
00:07:55,416 --> 00:07:57,041
Cheng Fan betrayed Lao Bai.

127
00:07:57,416 --> 00:07:58,958
He can betray you just as easily.

128
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:01,000
That's a lie!

129
00:08:01,250 --> 00:08:03,125
I've never thought of betraying him.

130
00:08:03,750 --> 00:08:04,750
Zhao Lingye,

131
00:08:04,875 --> 00:08:06,457
do you dare to deny
that in these three years,

132
00:08:06,458 --> 00:08:08,166
you've never doubted him?

133
00:08:17,208 --> 00:08:18,208
I trust him.

134
00:08:19,583 --> 00:08:20,583
Cheng Fan,

135
00:08:21,125 --> 00:08:22,415
Lao Bai killed my parents,

136
00:08:22,416 --> 00:08:23,750
and he killed your mother too.

137
00:08:23,916 --> 00:08:25,500
Why are you still working for them?

138
00:08:25,708 --> 00:08:27,041
He's not like Lao Bai.

139
00:08:28,333 --> 00:08:29,333
He's different.

140
00:08:30,625 --> 00:08:32,916
If Zhao Lingye dares to kill
Zhou Chen and me today,

141
00:08:33,583 --> 00:08:35,208
he'll kill you tomorrow.

142
00:08:35,625 --> 00:08:38,250
To them, human lives are just tools.

143
00:08:40,625 --> 00:08:42,833
He never loved you.

144
00:08:48,166 --> 00:08:49,833
I didn't want to kill anyone today.

145
00:09:00,875 --> 00:09:01,875
Bai Che!

146
00:09:04,291 --> 00:09:06,250
Stop!

147
00:09:06,708 --> 00:09:08,125
Let me go!

148
00:10:25,875 --> 00:10:26,875
Bai Che.

149
00:10:32,833 --> 00:10:33,833
It's nothing.

150
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:35,208
I'm just worried about you.

151
00:10:51,666 --> 00:10:53,106
It's going to be very unsafe lately.

152
00:10:53,791 --> 00:10:54,791
Would you...

153
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:57,666
like to move in with me?

154
00:11:47,166 --> 00:11:48,332
I'm glad

155
00:11:48,333 --> 00:11:49,333
you came to see me.

156
00:11:50,083 --> 00:11:51,083
But next time,

157
00:11:51,666 --> 00:11:52,666
just call me.

158
00:11:53,166 --> 00:11:54,166
I'll come pick you up.

159
00:11:58,250 --> 00:11:59,250
Can you feel it?

160
00:12:00,583 --> 00:12:01,583
Every time he sees you,

161
00:12:02,916 --> 00:12:04,083
it beats a little faster.

162
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:54,700
(To be continued)

